  "official_title": "A bill to amend the Clean Air Act to provide for further assessment of the validity of the theory concerning depletion of ozone in the stratosphere by halocarbon compounds before proceeding with any further regulation of such compounds, to provide for needed further research and study, and for other purposes.", 
